NARRATOR:<i> And neither are you,</i>

33:00.019 --> 33:02.188
<i>Brit. Come on.</i>

33:02.188 --> 33:05.400
I mean, did you guys know

33:02.188 --> 33:05.400
each other? Come on.

33:05.400 --> 33:07.861
What happened?

33:05.400 --> 33:07.861
What happened is he betrayed me

33:07.861 --> 33:09.362
and backstabbed me like

33:09.362 --> 33:11.197
the backstabbing betrayer

33:09.362 --> 33:11.197
that he is.

33:11.197 --> 33:12.783
Can you be a little more

33:11.197 --> 33:12.783
specific?

33:12.783 --> 33:14.242
Ask him what happened

33:12.783 --> 33:14.242
the last time

33:14.242 --> 33:15.744
we went shopping

33:14.242 --> 33:15.744
in Mexico City.

33:15.744 --> 33:17.203
Huh.

33:17.203 --> 33:18.538
I forgot all about that.

33:18.538 --> 33:21.458
<i>What did you do?</i>

33:18.538 --> 33:21.458
I...

33:21.458 --> 33:24.377
I tipped off the paparazzi.

33:21.458 --> 33:24.377
<i>What?</i>

33:24.377 --> 33:26.880
I was still a C-plus-lister

33:24.377 --> 33:26.880
at the time

33:26.880 --> 33:28.381
and I knew that being

33:26.880 --> 33:28.381
photographed

33:28.381 --> 33:29.842
with Britney would help my

33:28.381 --> 33:29.842
career.

33:29.842 --> 33:31.885
<i>Yes. How could you do that?</i>

33:31.885 --> 33:35.347
I'm so sorry, Brit.

33:35.347 --> 33:36.849
Now that I'm mega-famous,

33:36.849 --> 33:39.309
I understand what

33:36.849 --> 33:39.309
a mega-transgression that was.

33:39.309 --> 33:41.979
<i>I trusted you, Ro.</i>

33:39.309 --> 33:41.979
I'm so ashamed.

33:41.979 --> 33:44.815
And I totally get why

33:41.979 --> 33:44.815
you changed the teleprompter.

33:44.815 --> 33:46.483
<i>I didn't exactly change it,</i>

33:44.815 --> 33:46.483
<i>though.</i>

33:46.483 --> 33:48.401
<i>See, I was just sad</i>

33:46.483 --> 33:48.401
<i>about your betrayal</i>

33:48.401 --> 33:50.069
<i>and the teleprompter guy</i>

33:48.401 --> 33:50.069
<i>overheard,</i>

33:50.069 --> 33:52.071
<i>and I think he was trying</i>

33:50.069 --> 33:52.071
<i>to impress me.</i>

33:52.071 --> 33:55.325
<i>He was a real sweetie,</i>

33:52.071 --> 33:55.325
<i>you know? Yeah.</i>

33:55.325 --> 34:00.747
Well, from the bottom

33:55.325 --> 34:00.747
of my broken heart, I'm sorry.

34:00.747 --> 34:02.457
And I hope that our friendship

34:02.457 --> 34:04.751
could be as strong

34:02.457 --> 34:04.751
as it once was.

34:04.751 --> 34:07.420
<i>You know,</i>

34:04.751 --> 34:07.420
<i>I think it'll even be stronger.</i>

34:07.420 --> 34:09.422
<i>Stronger than yesterday.</i>

34:09.422 --> 34:11.008
[♪♪]

34:11.008 --> 34:12.759
I'm on desk? Why?

34:12.759 --> 34:14.636
Because you let

34:12.759 --> 34:14.636
Nadine Hansan walk.

34:14.636 --> 34:16.221
You knew that.

34:14.636 --> 34:16.221
We were tracking her.

34:16.221 --> 34:18.264
I'm talking about

34:16.221 --> 34:18.264
the first time you did it.

34:18.264 --> 34:20.475
It's about Nadine.

34:18.264 --> 34:20.475
Your old partner?

34:20.475 --> 34:21.935
It's that I let her go.

34:21.935 --> 34:23.269
Sorry, Cordero,

34:23.269 --> 34:24.563
an informant's come forward.

34:24.563 --> 34:26.147
Who?

34:26.147 --> 34:28.859
Tell me, who was it?

34:28.859 --> 34:32.153
Is that thing on?

34:28.859 --> 34:32.153
Scott, I don't care.

34:35.240 --> 34:36.825
Look, he wants to

34:35.240 --> 34:36.825
remain anonymous.

34:36.825 --> 34:38.159
I gave him my word.

34:44.457 --> 34:46.167
[♪♪]

34:57.930 --> 34:59.681
Oh, well.

34:59.681 --> 35:02.225
She said she'd keep Milos away

34:59.681 --> 35:02.225
from Mateo, at least.

35:10.525 --> 35:13.403
What the hell, man?

35:10.525 --> 35:13.403
Hey. Get off me. Hold this.

35:13.403 --> 35:16.322
Milos, Petra,

35:16.322 --> 35:20.159
we are here

35:16.322 --> 35:20.159
on that most momentous of days.

35:20.159 --> 35:22.662
You turned me in? You did!

35:20.159 --> 35:22.662
What are you talking about?

35:22.662 --> 35:25.331
Michael, calm down.

35:22.662 --> 35:25.331
Oh, no. This ass cost me my job.

35:25.331 --> 35:27.375
Remember what I told you

35:25.331 --> 35:27.375
on the monitor, Jane?

35:27.375 --> 35:31.880
I, Milos,

35:27.375 --> 35:31.880
promise not to forsake you.

35:31.880 --> 35:33.172
You let Nadine go?

35:33.172 --> 35:34.883
Don't pretend

35:33.172 --> 35:34.883
you didn't know.

35:34.883 --> 35:36.468
You knew this?

35:34.883 --> 35:36.468
I mean, yes, he told me.

35:36.468 --> 35:38.303
These people kidnapped Mateo.

35:38.303 --> 35:39.638
Don't pretend you didn't know.

35:39.638 --> 35:42.265
I didn't know!

35:39.638 --> 35:42.265
Stop, Michael, stop!

35:42.265 --> 35:44.183
Stop! No!

35:45.852 --> 35:48.647
No! No!

35:48.647 --> 35:50.941
[CRYING]

35:50.941 --> 35:53.652
Mateo. Are you okay?

35:53.652 --> 35:55.361
Oh, my God.

35:57.238 --> 35:59.449
[♪♪]

35:59.449 --> 36:00.909
Should be fine.

36:00.909 --> 36:02.661
Dr. Garcia said to bring him

36:00.909 --> 36:02.661
in tomorrow

36:02.661 --> 36:05.163
if it doesn't look better.

36:05.163 --> 36:08.625
How did this happen?

36:05.163 --> 36:08.625
I told you, that guy hates me.

36:10.627 --> 36:13.046
What?

36:10.627 --> 36:13.046
Did you do it?

36:13.046 --> 36:14.673
Excuse me?

36:14.673 --> 36:17.759
You were there.

36:14.673 --> 36:17.759
Of course I didn't do it.

36:17.759 --> 36:20.345
See, this-- This is why

36:17.759 --> 36:20.345
I said he's bad for us.

36:20.345 --> 36:22.597
He's making you doubt me.

36:20.345 --> 36:22.597
Sorry.

36:24.099 --> 36:26.309
But you still think I did it.

36:29.437 --> 36:30.689
[LAUGHTER]

36:30.689 --> 36:32.983
[SPEAKING SPANISH] We did it!

36:30.689 --> 36:32.983
Whoo!

36:34.109 --> 36:36.569
Did what?

36:34.109 --> 36:36.569
Zed is gonna admit

36:36.569 --> 36:39.114
that he stole the ring.

36:36.569 --> 36:39.114
What? How?

36:39.114 --> 36:42.617
Admit what you did

36:39.114 --> 36:42.617
or the masterpiece is toast!

36:42.617 --> 36:44.577
And I'll call the cops

36:44.577 --> 36:46.746
and tell them

36:44.577 --> 36:46.746
about your little side business,

36:46.746 --> 36:48.289
Jon Snow!

36:48.289 --> 36:50.042
Wow.

36:50.042 --> 36:51.584
Good job.

36:51.584 --> 36:53.086
[LAUGHING]

36:54.671 --> 36:56.422
I owe you an apology, Xiomara.

36:56.422 --> 36:59.384
You? No. I almost blew it

36:56.422 --> 36:59.384
for you.

36:59.384 --> 37:02.428
This all happened on June 12th.

37:04.056 --> 37:05.807
Wait, what's June 12th?

37:07.392 --> 37:10.103
The anniversary

37:07.392 --> 37:10.103
of your Grandpa Mateo's death.

37:11.146 --> 37:13.690
Mommy.

37:13.690 --> 37:16.902
Ma, wanna go eat

37:13.690 --> 37:16.902
at La Rosa tonight, maybe?

37:19.404 --> 37:23.241
Ma, come on,

37:19.404 --> 37:23.241
I know you can hear me.

37:23.241 --> 37:25.869
Not tonight, Xiomara.

37:33.376 --> 37:35.670
You wanted to go

37:33.376 --> 37:35.670
to his favorite restaurant.

37:35.670 --> 37:36.922
Yeah, well--

37:36.922 --> 37:40.258
And I was so consumed

37:36.922 --> 37:40.258
in my own grief.

37:40.258 --> 37:43.178
I should have been there

37:40.258 --> 37:43.178
for you.

37:43.178 --> 37:46.598
What type of mother

37:43.178 --> 37:46.598
doesn't put her child first?

37:48.183 --> 37:49.851
Please forgive me, my child.

37:49.851 --> 37:51.477
Stop.

37:51.477 --> 37:55.148
Ma, you've made it up to me

37:51.477 --> 37:55.148
a thousand times over.

37:59.861 --> 38:01.613
[CRYING]

38:01.613 --> 38:05.951
Oh. It's okay. Yeah.

38:01.613 --> 38:05.951
Mommy's here.

38:05.951 --> 38:08.369
[GASPS]

38:05.951 --> 38:08.369
What happened to his arm?

38:08.369 --> 38:11.248
Michael and Rafael got

38:08.369 --> 38:11.248
into an awful fight.

38:11.248 --> 38:12.832
Like a real physical fight.

38:12.832 --> 38:16.377
NARRATOR:

38:12.832 --> 38:16.377
<i>And so Jane told them</i>

38:12.832 --> 38:16.377
<i>what happened.</i>

38:20.423 --> 38:21.925
<i>How ugly it got.</i>

38:24.469 --> 38:27.555
<i>And how she thought Rafael</i>

38:24.469 --> 38:27.555
<i>probably turned Michael in.</i>

38:27.555 --> 38:30.475
WOMAN:

38:27.555 --> 38:30.475
<i>Go ahead and take a seat.</i>

38:30.475 --> 38:32.393
NARRATOR:

38:30.475 --> 38:32.393
<i>But I don't need to tell you,</i>

38:32.393 --> 38:33.895
<i>that guy is not Rafael.</i>

38:33.895 --> 38:35.396
WOMAN:

38:33.895 --> 38:35.396
<i>State your name for the record.</i>

38:35.396 --> 38:37.274
<i>I'm Eric Wu</i>

38:37.274 --> 38:39.901
<i>and I'm here to talk about</i>

38:37.274 --> 38:39.901
<i>my friend, Nadine Hansan.</i>

38:43.238 --> 38:44.864
It...

38:45.865 --> 38:47.200
It wasn't Rafael.

38:48.576 --> 38:51.163
What?

38:48.576 --> 38:51.163
I...

38:51.163 --> 38:53.206
I watched one of the interviews

38:53.206 --> 38:55.834
and it was this guy,

38:53.206 --> 38:55.834
Nadine's friend.

38:55.834 --> 38:57.418
Oh, my God, I accused him.

38:57.418 --> 38:59.796
I am so sorry, Jane.

38:57.418 --> 38:59.796
I screwed up.

38:59.796 --> 39:01.173
You know, the way I--

39:01.173 --> 39:03.549
The way I feel about Rafael,

39:01.173 --> 39:03.549
it--

39:03.549 --> 39:06.469
It clouded my judgment.

39:06.469 --> 39:08.680
And mine.

39:08.680 --> 39:10.223
And that man

39:08.680 --> 39:10.223
you attacked tonight,

39:10.223 --> 39:13.392
the man that clouds

39:10.223 --> 39:13.392
your judgment,

39:13.392 --> 39:14.811
that's Mateo's father.

39:16.188 --> 39:17.480
I know. I know.

39:17.480 --> 39:19.191
I mean,

39:17.480 --> 39:19.191
I'll work on my anger.

39:19.191 --> 39:22.861
How? Think about

39:19.191 --> 39:22.861
what happened tonight.

39:22.861 --> 39:24.988
Mateo was hurt.

39:24.988 --> 39:27.907
Michael, he was hurt.

39:29.075 --> 39:30.493
[CRYING]

39:30.493 --> 39:32.912
NARRATOR:<i> And at that moment,</i>

39:30.493 --> 39:32.912
<i>Jane saw it.</i>

39:36.582 --> 39:40.003
Which is why we won't work.

39:36.582 --> 39:40.003
Please.

39:40.003 --> 39:41.921
You should go.

39:55.393 --> 39:57.687
You okay?

39:57.687 --> 39:59.981
I will be.

39:59.981 --> 40:01.691
But you're getting

39:59.981 --> 40:01.691
your green card,

40:01.691 --> 40:04.485
so let's focus on that, okay?

40:01.691 --> 40:04.485
Okay.

40:04.485 --> 40:07.446
My Mateo would like that.

40:07.446 --> 40:12.660
I can feel him smiling down

40:07.446 --> 40:12.660
