40:12.660 --> 40:14.746
And smiling up at us.

40:14.746 --> 40:16.122
Look.

40:16.122 --> 40:17.999
Your first smile.

40:17.999 --> 40:19.458
Look at you.

40:19.458 --> 40:21.586
NARRATOR:<i> It was a day</i>

40:19.458 --> 40:21.586
<i>the Villanueva women</i>

40:21.586 --> 40:23.588
<i>would always remember</i>

40:23.588 --> 40:27.842
<i>because Jane meticulously</i>

40:23.588 --> 40:27.842
<i>documented it in her baby book.</i>

40:30.511 --> 40:33.514
<i>It was also a day</i>

40:30.511 --> 40:33.514
<i>Petra would always remember.</i>

40:33.514 --> 40:35.558
Good night, Milos.

40:33.514 --> 40:35.558
Petra.

40:35.558 --> 40:38.937
There is something

40:35.558 --> 40:38.937
I must tell you.

40:38.937 --> 40:42.232
The marriage, it wasn't

40:38.937 --> 40:42.232
just about tax shelter.

40:42.232 --> 40:44.317
Yes, I know, Milos.

40:42.232 --> 40:44.317
You have feelings for me.

40:44.317 --> 40:46.152
Yes.

40:46.152 --> 40:50.615
But I also have 2,000 live-fire

40:46.152 --> 40:50.615
hand grenades in these boxes.

40:50.615 --> 40:52.284
What?

40:52.284 --> 40:55.120
Wedding provided perfect cover

40:52.284 --> 40:55.120
