41:00.125 --> 41:04.462
Spousal privilege.

41:00.125 --> 41:04.462
It is, how you say? A "vin-vin."

41:04.462 --> 41:05.838
NARRATOR:

41:04.462 --> 41:05.838
<i>Wow.</i>

41:05.838 --> 41:07.382
<i>Talk about dropping a bomb.</i>

